    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">Weapon attacks and jutsus that use your Sword of Exorcism can always careful cast around any non Aberrations, Celestials, Demons, Otsutsuki or Monstrosities, it can Interact with any non physical creatures such as ghosts or phantasms, It can be used in place of Cross Spear for any Walker clan hijutsu, it can use constitution for the heavy property and it counts as your Innocence (Cross) and an odachi for the sake of interacting with features and jutsus. Additionally a number of times per rest equal to your constitution modifier when you would deal damage with this weapon you can deal additional damage as chakra damage equal to half the original damage, You do not need to expend the use of this feature to activate it when you would deal damage to a Aberrations, Celestials, Demons, Otsutsuki or Monstrosity.</span></p>",
